                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                                <span>Use clear, high-quality images to showcase your work</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                                <span>Be specific about what you're offering in your title</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
